                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": "The paladin casts <i>delay poison </i>and <i>protection from energy </i>(electricity and fire) on herself, and <i>greater magic weapon </i>on her greatsword."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The paladin targets the most powerful creature present or an obviously demonic target. She uses her divine bond to add the <i>brilliant energy</i>, <i>holy</i>, <i>keen</i>, and <i>speed </i>special abilities to her greatsword as appropriate, and uses mercies to counteract any negative conditions or afflictions she gains."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Base Statistics",
                "text": "Without <i>delay poison</i>, <i>greater magic weapon</i>, and <i>protection from energy</i>, the paladin\u2019s statistics are <b>Immune </b>charm, compulsion, disease, fear; <b>Resist </b>none; <b>Melee</b><i>+1 cold iron evil outsider-bane greatsword </i>+29/+24/+19/+14 (2d6+11/17\u201320)."
